<section class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-sage-100 text-sage-700 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Our design philosophy
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 leading-tight mb-6">
          Designing against<br />
          <span class="text-primary-600">paralysis</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Decision fatigue and task paralysis are real barriers for ADHD brains. Every design choice in Tidy — from color to copy to interaction — was made to lower friction, not just add features.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          This is the story of how we rethought the cleaning app from the ground up, with neurodivergent users leading the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Video player -->
      <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl shadow-stone-200 border border-stone-100 bg-stone-900">
        <video
          controls
          preload="metadata"
          class="w-full block"
        >
          <source src="/videos/Designing_Against_Paralysis.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
